author: Deepika Jayaram
title: Manju Warrier mimicks Mohanlal like a boss!
text:
Looks like the dubsmash fever has gripped Manju Warrier and Rima Kallingal too.
As per the promo of the reality show, the actors will be seen dubsmashing a dialogue from Aaram Thampuran.
The Ennum Eppozhum actor is seen replicating Mohanlal's mannerisms, as she delivers the dialogue, "Thampuran...Kanimangalam Kovilathe Jagannathan Thampuran... ", with much verve.
